	   <tr><td colspan=2>as of 2-1-03 it still drops off Bro. Z I know not everyone approves of this method for obtaining this robe, but to each there own. Placeholders for him are, Drake (just plain drake) Maldyn the unkempt and Hasten Bootstrutter. Respawn of mobs are approx 15min after death. I have killed him 3 times before i got the robe. Something that i heard RIGHT before killing him the last time was... If he pops WHILE you are ALREADY in the zone, and graphic shows him wearing the robe..then he will drop it. If you zone in and he is already up..doesnt matter how he looks..he might or might not have it. THIS IS JUST SOMETHING I HEARD!! When i killed him last time he popped while we were in zone and he was wearing it and it DID drop..just fyi. I hope this helps.<br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Sat Feb&nbsp;&nbsp;1 01:17:48 2003</em><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
