uests yourself you lazy pieces o' crap!  I have said what I wanted, flame away.<br><br>Gesthal Vecter - Current 44 Monk of Xegony.<br>(Wow, that was long ;)<br>&nbsp;<br>To all you Non-Monks, you can't FD when 7 Wizzies are chain-casting on you.&nbsp;&nbsp;FD explained. =)</td></tr>
